memberdef.initializer: OBJ* L_##NAME(OBJ* o)\ {\ OBJ* ret = empty_obj();\ o = preeval(o);\ ret->type = o->type;\ if (ret->type == T_NUM)\ ret->num = o->num;\ \ NEXT(o);\ if (o == NULL) return ret; \ \ ITERATE_OBJECT(o, curr)\ {\ \ if (ret->type == T_NUM && curr->type == T_NUM)\ ret->num SIGN##= curr->num;\ }\ return ret;\ }
